[Possible Modifications] :
Add a database to store and manage data about cars, employees, and customers who have a bank account.

Create a new class called Customer to store customer details, including employee ID, their record in the company, and whether they have purchased a car before.

Add a repair and maintenance workshop module to handle car service requests.

Extend the Person class to create Employee subclasses, such as hourly-based employees and daily-based employees.
